{"tid":1516900,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"深水埗英勇狗號33768 係陳國興高級警員","createTime":"2019-08-29T17:25:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-30T06:24:16.000Z","uid":280488,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"53e330e63ec9d1ce456597cd3200787b3459a799","tid":1516900,"uid":280488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T17:25:56.000Z","msg":"【2358 深水埗】多名警員四面八方包抄拘捕在深水埗的市民。有母親在現場高叫兒子的名字，表示與自己的兒子失去聯絡。<br />\n<br />\n但現場一眾警員沒有馬上提供協助，反而大叫「係咪阻礙警員執行職務？」更包圍她。在場該母親的女兒叫警員「唔好搞我媽咪」。眾警員包圍擾攘一輪後才有一名白衫警員介入，抄下該名女士兒子的名字「幫忙問吓」。<br />\n<br />\n但後來，該名母親拒絕離去，一名警員在極近距離用大支的胡椒噴霧直接指向她面部，大叫「你個仔唔喺度啊」。<br />\n<br />\n蘋果Facebook: <a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=10158003338362448&amp;id=105259197447\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D10158003338362448%26id%3D105259197447&d=uSpWWhS%2FFNP1%2BK4afk1FkL32HZRMtn4xjJY4gFhUisg%3D&h=4d7bfdd1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=10158003338362448&amp;id=105259197447</a>"},{"pid":"d27731b9e652404c237aa8572aea2c97e493b5f4","tid":1516900,"uid":8482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T17:28:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1c2c68ba0d0085fa75c0a51e356f97048bc62ef","tid":1516900,"uid":101498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T17:28:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5eD5qRC.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5eD5qRC.png&h=9cefd6db&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ugkC1pY.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FugkC1pY.png&h=1efec83e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bffcfcd07b5e7a033ba095e9a54c7c4a49349101","tid":1516900,"uid":280488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T17:30:10.000Z","msg":"自推1"},{"pid":"3